{"word":"G1473 - ἐγώ - egṓ - eg-o' - I","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐγώ</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">egṓ</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">eg-o'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">I</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>NA / Not Available</span>"},{"paragraph":"நான், எனக்கு - பிரதி பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":"personal pronoun, I"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>A primary pronoun of the first person, &ldquo;I&rdquo; (only expressed when emphatic): - I, me. For the other cases and the plural see <a href=\"#/G1691 - ἐμέ - emé - em-eh'/1691\">G1691</a>, <a href=\"#/G1698 - ἐμοί - emoí - em-oy'/1698\">G1698</a>, <a href=\"#/G1700 - ἐμοῦ - emoû - em-oo'/1700\">G1700</a>, <a href=\"#/G2248 - ἡμᾶς - hēmâs - hay-mas'/2248\">G2248</a>, <a href=\"#/G2249 - ἡμεῖς - hēmeîs - hay-mice'/2249\">G2249</a>, <a href=\"#/G2254 - ἡμῖν - hēmîn - hay-meen'/2254\">G2254</a>, <a href=\"#/G2257 - ἡμῶν - hēmōn - hay-mone'/2257\">G2257</a>, etc.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}